{
  "stem": "15962.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was very, very strenuous work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And each shift-- they were working in three shifts-- each shift had to work-- walk down to the station, through this cute little street.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So these inhabitants saw the prisoners march by three times to work and three times back, literally six times a day.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Each shift brought back many dead that died during their shift.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They also had to wait at the railway station for quite a while in inclement weather, in both directions.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So the death rate was very high.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was a small crematorium also, to deal with the dead.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the very sick were periodically shipped to Mauthausen for extermination.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Mauthausen did have a gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The group of boys that was interspersed with the rest of the men came for work there was assigned various tasks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I recall that most of the time, we were sitting in some damp, dark space, peeling rotten potatoes that were mostly blue.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Part of the time I was employed as an orderly for a group of French electricians that were responsible for all the lighting, including electrified fences and some other work outside the camp for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they treated me very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I wish that long after the war I would have been able to connect with any of those survivors.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Interestingly, when we were in Mauthausen last year, there was a large group of French people who came.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "A couple of them were survivors, and a few were wives or children of survivors.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they told us that they came back to Mauthausen every year as the commemoration.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they were in Melk as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I was there only for a short time, unable to really make any direct connections.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
